data.description: Check out this captivating 4-bed, 2.5-bath residence spanning an impressive 3,304 sq ft. The Master Suite welcomes you with a vaulted ceiling, offering a retreat within your own homeCoa haven of peace and tranquility. Located in a community that prioritizes safety, enjoy the convenience of a monitored school bus stop for added peace of mind. Proximity to the airport and shopping destinations ensures that your daily needs are met with ease. Embrace the lifestyle you deserveCoschedule a private tour to experience the seamless blend of elegance and convenience that defines this extraordinary property. NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
